Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影待你很信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种信赖何时建
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.04,0:00:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟婆婆约好的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.73,0:00:18.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在当上火影之前 我绝对不会死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我很感兴趣 真是意味又深长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 火影婆婆将赌注押在了我的身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.08,0:00:27.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把约定的信物交给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.44,0:00:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如皆人坚信的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:42.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让鸣人参战 才能保护忍者 保护大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.46,0:00:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我赌鸣人赢 你认为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.18,0:00:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么时候开始打算赌鸣人一次的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.42,0:00:57.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他击败佩因 成为村子英雄的时候吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.48,0:00:59.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 比那次早很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.70,0:01:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影根本就是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.50,0:01:11.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有傻瓜才会做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:17.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当着我的面侮辱三代爷爷和四代的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.38,0:01:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是女人我也不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:22.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要揍扁你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.19,0:01:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你被我打晕前我想问你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.30,0:01:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么如此执着于火影的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.42,0:01:50.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要得到火影的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为…火影是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就来打个赌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.84,0:02:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打赌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:11.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能在一周内掌握这个忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就承认你能够成为火影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.74,0:02:15.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并把这个首饰送给你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:19.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那场赌局鸣人赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时起 你就将赌注押在他身上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.79,0:02:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老夫第一次见你时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:37.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只不过赌赌骰子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.31,0:02:43.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时的我也只有钱可赌了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.83,0:04:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,5,,纲手大人 请等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点啦 静音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个赌场…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:25.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 旅店可不会等我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅店才不会跑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.44,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:33.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人 刚刚是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与我们无关 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老大 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干吗 萨基
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:03.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是些无聊的事我揍扁你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:05.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是无聊的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.08,0:05:05.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:13.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.69,0:05:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 你不是认识才叫我的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是想烘托下气氛 让老大更有面子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.15,0:05:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 我打扁你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.92,0:05:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偷笑了 老大
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然会笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说中的肥羊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发财啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些全部换成筹码
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.59,0:06:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.11,0:06:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你玩得尽兴才对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必尽兴 敞开玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.46,0:06:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全被当成冤大头了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.94,0:06:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有尸体 看来敌人逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 那些家伙将苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:33.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(658,60)\fnsimhei\fs35}云隐这回三个龙套名字的意思是“苦辣甜”，为了延续一贯风格，继续意译。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之赶快去找甘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:47.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他应该在附近的旅店等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:50.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能很痛苦 你忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.04,0:07:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 买定离手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小 小 小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.59,0:07:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个一点 小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:09.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:17.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.50,0:07:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您究竟想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.36,0:07:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借来的钱已经输光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钱再借就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和谁借啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.09,0:07:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家旅馆住着一个叫纲手的女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸很大的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:36.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自己去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 你们是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:40.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨债的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.79,0:07:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我仔细搜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:50.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔 你们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:55.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是从金之国飞来的悍鸟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:08:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小妹妹 见过这个大婶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胸很大的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:07.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个漂亮姐姐在其他房间哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.33,0:08:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我帮你们去叫她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.10,0:08:17.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 小妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.94,0:08:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你手里那个亮晶晶的是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.00,0:08:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画像上那个漂亮姐姐给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:29.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说大姐姐遇上些破事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在山里大发脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.59,0:08:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在石头里发现很多这种亮晶晶的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.23,0:08:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.12,0:08:46.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为拿不下了 所以送了些给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那小鬼手上拿的可是金子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:09:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来纲手挖到金矿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.67,0:09:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.31,0:09:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在讨债就亏大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.03,0:09:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多借她钱 多赚利息才是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.42,0:09:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正肯定能讨回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借她借她 多借点给她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:21.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位债主大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:24.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳烦你们远道而来 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天的赌本也筹好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 去喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:37.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是诈骗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没骗人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.98,0:09:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实在山上打碎岩石后发现了金子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只有这么点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.72,0:09:47.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说有很多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在拓山挖到的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.74,0:09:50.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(638,60)\fnsimhei\fs40}“拓山”读音同“很多”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是甘吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.12,0:10:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏雷影大人引开了敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才能平安完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.72,0:10:15.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于拿到杉之国的秘传忍法帖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在还不能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.35,0:10:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 别小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:46.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷鼠激震
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.53,0:10:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.03,0:10:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来 别靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个虫状的肿块在作怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肿块里注入了会引爆的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:15.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够吸收附身之人的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:18.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要累积到一定量便会爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您刚刚说苦最后用了忍术吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:27.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦使用忍术便会放出大量的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:30.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肿块吸收查克拉后迅速变大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会爆炸吗 甘有救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.18,0:11:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单凭我的医疗忍术…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.02,0:11:41.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕心有余而力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有个人肯定能救他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她就在这个镇上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.44,0:11:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.07,0:11:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的纲手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世上没有比纲手大人更厉害的医疗忍者了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:02.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很天真呢 甘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但纲手大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.53,0:12:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别对其他村的忍者如此尊敬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶和云隐的关系如此之差
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她怎么可能愿意救我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.31,0:12:26.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我会让她救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.60,0:12:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何也要把纲手带过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:31.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可以 雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能为了我去求其他村的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让她救你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:43.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您想舍弃作为雷影的荣耀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既不会舍弃 也要救活你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您真的比甘还天真
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:54.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对部下见死不救算什么荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么资格当雷影
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛 我不准你死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:02.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定要和我一起平安返回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷影大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走 甘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带我去找纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静音 酒没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:20.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酒 酒没了 拿酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:29.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这么点就倒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.67,0:13:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 是初代火影 爷爷的项链
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:49.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你了 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.66,0:13:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要像爷爷一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天要继承火影的名号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.13,0:13:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为火影是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次也好 让我看看他的笑脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢村子和同伴们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想保护他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从妹妹死了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.92,0:14:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这份感情就成为了我的支柱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.62,0:14:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人跟我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要成为火影
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为保护大家的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为火影是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.93,0:14:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个送给你 希望你能收下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火影根本就是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西当不当才没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.70,0:15:15.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只希望你们能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.07,0:15:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想再次见到你们 拥抱你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶传说中的三忍之一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人 我等有事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您务必…务必答应我的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是云隐的忍者 甘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.55,0:15:44.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请用您那卓越的医疗忍术救救我的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.66,0:15:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是云隐的医疗忍者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴受伤 你去医治不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.44,0:16:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下心有余而力不足
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.45,0:16:07.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,云隐的人有什么资格来求木叶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:15.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这群想窃取日向白眼的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此事双方已经解决了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.74,0:16:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得了便宜还卖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:23.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不计前嫌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了 甘
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.39,0:16:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始我就认为你不会乖乖合作的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们云隐的首领 雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真来了一位厉害的大人物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.26,0:16:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿意我就逼你就范
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:17:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是对谁说话呢 别后悔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在后面的空地等你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个臭女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.29,0:17:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋 竟敢放我鸽子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会善罢甘休的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快起来 起来和我战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:52.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是云隐的雷影大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:01.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真来了一位…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.91,0:18:03.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话你昨天就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别生气 别生气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.39,0:18:09.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 我们来赌一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.05,0:18:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说要来硬的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果扳手腕能赢我就答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我睡着的时候究竟发生了什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:54.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,力量竟然在我之上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.63,0:18:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:04.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能输 老夫如果在这里输掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决不能输啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纲手大人竟然输在力量上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙一决胜负的瞬间松了手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我俩的手之间制造了空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:45.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一瞬间再利用手的加速度扳了回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:49.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙并非力量胜过了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.36,0:19:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是以速度取胜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可别说我卑鄙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.28,0:19:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会的 我也没说比力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:02.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你扳手腕赢了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.29,0:20:04.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那您愿意为辛治疗了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.06,0:20:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.74,0:20:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 静音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把最强的医疗忍者纲手大人带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.13,0:20:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们夺取了杉之国的秘术是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杉之国竟然还有这等高手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方并非杉隐的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.43,0:20:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.32,0:20:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杉隐雇来的轩辕众
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:50.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轩辕众
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:54.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传闻中专门猎杀忍者的轩辕众吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在治疗中出错就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:03.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把经过如实告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.20,0:22:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆裂虫通过简单的手术应该就能取出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.70,0:22:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那纲手卡莱伊就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.93,0:22:44.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静音你来做手术
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 为什么你不主刀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.13,0:22:50.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心 静音也是优秀的医疗忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.54,0:22:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你来…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.29,0:22:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 这里就给静音了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:56.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集「火影忍者 疾风传」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「值得下赌注之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:02.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莱伊要是有个万一我可饶不了你
